Big Data 2015 - A Study of linguistic drift - Sentences Length - Gil Brechb√ºhler

The code in the src folder is a mapreduce code which for each year outputs a file (actually one file by year by reducer)
containing :
sentence_length \t number_of_sentences_of_this_length

It takes as argument :
	- the input folder
	- the output folder

A call sample :

hadoop jar Sentence.jar ch.epfl.bigdata.sentence.Sentence /projects/dh-shared/* /projects/linguistic-shift/stats/sentences-length-test 

Note that the input folder is read recursively.